    "Management": {
      "text": "I&D\n- longitudinal incision lateral to sacral midline\nAntibiotics\nonly needed if\ncellulitis\nis present\nRefer to surgeon for recurrent disease\n40% recurrence rate\nRefer for follicle removal after acute inflammation subsides (~1 wk)\n[1]",
